- "Attracting more than one suitor" means the style has been ordered more than once;
- "Popularity" is determined by the number of orders.

- 'Shipped' orders refer to orders that have been dispatched to customers;
- 'Total sales' is calculated as the product of the quantity and price for each clothing item;
- 'Since the start of this year' refers to orders placed on or after January 1, 2023.
